---
Checks: >
  -*,
  bugprone-*,
  clang-analyzer-*,
  cppcoreguidelines-*,
  google-*,
  misc-*,
  modernize-*,
  performance-*,
  portability-*,
  readability-*,
  -misc-no-recursion,
  -modernize-use-trailing-return-type,
  -readability-implicit-bool*,
  -readability-named-parameter

HeaderFilterRegex: '\(src\)\/*.\(h|hpp\)'
CheckOptions:
  readability-function-size.LineThreshold:                40
  readability-identifier-naming.VariableCase:             lower_case
  readability-identifier-length.MinimumLoopCounterNameLength: 1
...
